{"tid":1639701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捐助被警槍傷印尼女記者","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T17:20:14.000Z","uid":30647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"978e1a62583fdd4caaa61499279de7c9059b42f9","tid":1639701,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tXvLBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tXvLBR.jpg&h=562b8b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會將發放一萬元緊急撥款予疑受警察槍傷而失明的女記者Veby Indah，以解燃眉之急。同時，其代表律師及本會近期亦收到不少市民表達捐助之意。Veby Indah已確認同意由記協代收公眾捐款，所有捐款將全數交予Veby Indah作為生活、醫療及緊急用途。<br />\n<br />\n至於Veby Indah擬就其傷勢提出訴訟，記協最近成立的「保護記者基金」將可提供有關司法程序的財政支援，倘Veby Indah提出申請，本會將一如處理其他求助個案，進行詳細審核，符合資格者將獲發放資助。<br />\n<br />\n有意捐款予Veby Indah的人士，請轉帳或存入記協的東亞銀行戶口：015-138-68-00541-8。<br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會<br />\n2019年10月8日<br />\n<br />\nSource: 記協 facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKJA.official/posts/10157393570810309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKJA.official%2Fposts%2F10157393570810309&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=108e409e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKJA.official/posts/10157393570810309</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKJA.official/photos/a.462959970308/10157393517855309/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKJA.official%2Fphotos%2Fa.462959970308%2F10157393517855309%2F&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=9b7353b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKJA.official/photos/a.462959970308/10157393517855309/</a>"},{"pid":"37b1883bf314b645a5147bf320089f3054548594","tid":1639701,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"892b0f4b8fba5cb673a802ac3a4ade0b758b71be","tid":1639701,"uid":168522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy